Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.11,0:00:14.04,Default_WMV_FHD_1920*1080_Microsoft YaHei,,0,0,0,,(出演 星野娜美)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.62,0:01:32.86,Default_WMV_FHD_1920*1080_Microsoft YaHei,,0,0,0,,高潮后顫抖小穴毫不留情繼續抽插\N怒濤再次激烈抽插性交
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.89,0:01:37.73,Default_WMV_FHD_1920*1080_Microsoft YaHei,,0,0,0,,  -早安  -早安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.09,0:01:41.03,Default_WMV_FHD_1920*1080_Microsoft YaHei,,0,0,0,,  -那個 這個是今天的腳本  -好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.40,0:01:42.50,Default_WMV_FHD_1920*1080_Microsoft YaHei,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.86,0:01:45.80,Default_WMV_FHD_1920*1080_Microsoft YaHei,,0,0,0,,是连續射精企劃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.17,0:01:51.67,Default_WMV_FHD_1920*1080_Microsoft YaHei,,0,0,0,,一般男優射一次結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.04,0:01:56.44,Default_WMV_FHD_1920*1080_Microsoft YaHei,,0,0,0,,但是今天需要他們\N數次高潮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.81,0:02:00.85,Default_WMV_FHD_1920*1080_Microsoft YaHei,,0,0,0,,做法就按照你的方式\N痴女的那種吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.58,0:02:02.68,Default_WMV_FHD_1920*1080_Microsoft YaHei,,0,0,0,,我喜歡的方式嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.05,0:02:05.99,Default_WMV_FHD_1920*1080_Microsoft YaHei,,0,0,0,,都可以 擼管或者口交都沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.72,0:02:08.92,Default_WMV_FHD_1920*1080_Microsoft YaHei,,0,0,0,,男優基本不能動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.29,0:02:12.59,Default_WMV_FHD_1920*1080_Microsoft YaHei,,0,0,0,,讓躺着的男優射出來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.96,0:02:15.53,Default_WMV_FHD_1920*1080_Microsoft YaHei,,0,0,0,,努力讓他們多射
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:19.20,Default_WMV_FHD_1920*1080_Microsoft YaHei,,0,0,0,,大概就是這樣\N(看來相信了是連射企劃)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.57,0:02:21.77,Default_WMV_FHD_1920*1080_Microsoft YaHei,,0,0,0,,  -知道了  -麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.77,0:02:23.61,Default_WMV_FHD_1920*1080_Microsoft YaHei,,0,0,0,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:33.15,Default_WMV_FHD_1920*1080_Microsoft YaHei,,0,0,0,,(真正要被追擊的人是星野本人)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.01,0:03:39.21,Default_WMV_FHD_1920*1080_Microsoft YaHei,,0,0,0,,預備 開始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.52,0:03:48.02,Default_WMV_FHD_1920*1080_Microsoft YaHei,,0,0,0,,今天只射一次的話\N可不會原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.23,0:03:57.93,Default_WMV_FHD_1920*1080_Microsoft YaHei,,0,0,0,,我會讓你多次射來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:15.92,Default_WMV_FHD_1920*1080_Microsoft YaHei,,0,0,0,,  -乳頭敏感嗎  -是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:25.83,Default_WMV_FHD_1920*1080_Microsoft YaHei,,0,0,0,,顫抖得好厲害
