Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:36.84,Default_WMV_FHD_1920*1080_Microsoft YaHei,,0,0,0,,  -忍不住了嗎  -是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.14,0:04:43.08,Default_WMV_FHD_1920*1080_Microsoft YaHei,,0,0,0,,  -這樣動我不方便舔  -好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.61,0:05:14.28,Default_WMV_FHD_1920*1080_Microsoft YaHei,,0,0,0,,  -好舒服  -舒服嗎\N  -是的
