Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.78,0:49:43.71,Default_WMV_FHD_1920*1080_Microsoft YaHei,,0,0,0,,  -但是你要忍住哦  -好
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.85,0:49:54.72,Default_WMV_FHD_1920*1080_Microsoft YaHei,,0,0,0,,  -這是什麼\N  -你覺得呢  -不知道
